Time-Stamp Protocol (TSP) package for Go

The package timestamp implements the Time-Stamp Protocol (TSP) as specified in RFC3161 (Internet X.509 Public Key
Infrastructure Time-Stamp Protocol (TSP)).

install:

`go install ./...`

usage:

```sh
$ timestamp-query -h
Usage of timestamp-query:
  -dump-body
    	dump body
  -raw
    	keep json raw output (no pretty)
  -request string
    	timestamp request, env TIMESTAMP_QUERY_REQUEST (default "ExampleCreateRequestParseResponse")
  -url string
    	timestamp server address, env TIMESTAMP_QUERY_URL (default "https://freetsa.org/tsr")
  -user string
    	username:password, env TIMESTAMP_QUERY_USER
```
